game.DiceyDescent.How.1: %s Choose a side to fall through
game.DiceyDescent.How.3: %s Make sure to choose the least bad sides to win!
deathMessages.DiceyDescent2: %s was too good of a conducter!
deathMessages.DiceyDescent3: %s was shocked at how good this map is...
deathMessages.DiceyDescent6: %s should not try enter the lottery...
game.ZombieTag.How.2: %s If a zombie attacks you, you will turn into a zombie too
game.BarrelDaredevil.How.1: %s Wait for the barrels to start falling
game.BarrelDaredevil.How.2: %s Click the button as late as you can to win
game.BarrelDaredevil.How.3: %s If you don't press the button in time you will lose!
deathMessages.BarrelDaredevil6: %s lived life too far on the edge
deathMessages.BarrelDaredevil8: %s would suck at find the button
game.BackAttack.How.1: %s Move left or right to change directions at the next turn
game.BackAttack.How.2: %s Click to shoot, try to hit the back of your opponents
game.LuckyLaunch.How.1: %s Choose your firework and activate it
game.LuckyLaunch.How.2: %s Each firework will randomly explode at different times
game.LuckyLaunch.How.3: %s The player whos firework explodes last wins!
game.LuckyLaunch.RightClickToLight: Go to your firework and %s to light it!
game.DerbyDash.How.1: %s Click to whip your horse, giving it a speed boost
game.DerbyDash.How.2: %s If you run out of stamina your speed will be reduced
game.DerbyDash.How.3: %s Your stamina generates quicker the longer it generates
game.DerbyDash.How.4: %s First horse to reach the end wins!
game.ChopChops.How.1: %s Left click your carrot to chop as quickly as you can
game.ChopChops.How.2: %s The first person to fully chop their carrot wins!
game.PopgunPosse.How.2: %s Shoot your can to keep it in the air and gain points
game.PopgunPosse.How.3: %s Dont let your can touch the ground!
game.FlagFracas.How.1: %s Look away from the flag until the game starts or you will be disqualified
game.FlagFracas.How.2: %s On go, turn around and sprint and jump to the flag as fast as you can
game.FlagFracas.How.3: %s First player to reach the flag wins!
game.FlagFracas.Disqual.1: All player except %s have been disqualified!
game.GoalGetters.How.1: %s Balls of different sizes will be flung at you
game.GoalGetters.How.2: %s Make sure you kick/punch the ball into the goal
game.GoalGetters.How.3: %s The player with the most goals wins!
game.RiskyRailway.How.1: %s Use your movement keys to choose a direction
game.RiskyRailway.How.2: %s One random direction will be blocked off
deathMessages.RiskyRailway6: %s should not try enter the lottery...
game.MazeDaze.How.1: %s Find your way through the maze
game.MazeDaze.How.2: %s Be careful as pads on the floor can change your controls
game.MazeDaze.How.3: %s First player to get to the centre wins!
game.HammerHeads.How.1: %s Whack the moles as they pop up
game.HammerHeads.How.2: %s Regular moles grant 1 point, golden moles grant 3, sus moles lose 3
game.HammerHeads.How.3: %s Whack other players to slow them down
game.HammerHeads.How.4: %s The player with the most points wins!
game.StopWatchers.How.1: %s Wait for your timer to disappear
game.StopWatchers.How.2: %s Right click once the specified time has passed
game.StopWatchers.How.3: %s The player closest to the target time wins!
game.FaceFlip.How.1: %s Choose a random card to flip
game.FaceFlip.How.2: %s If the card is yours, progress to the next line
game.FaceFlip.How.3: %s The first person to reach the last line wins!
game.WalkOff.How.1: %s Travel the distance listed above and right click once there
game.WalkOff.How.2: %s Use the signs to guide you
game.WalkOff.How.3: %s The player closest to the set distance wins!
game.TropicalPunch.How.1: %s Hold right click to charge your punch
game.TropicalPunch.How.2: %s Release to punch players infront of you
deathMessages.TropicalPunch8: Let's hope %s knows how to swim...
game.StrategySteps.How.1: %s Right Click to a number to select it
game.StrategySteps.How.2: %s If no one else chooses your number, move up the steps based on the chosen number
game.StrategySteps.How.3: %s First player to the top wins!
game.FriendlyFaceOff.How.1: %s Rearrange the pieces to mimic the image displayed
game.FriendlyFaceOff.How.2: %s You may need to change both their position and rotation
game.FriendlyFaceOff.How.3: %s Use right click to pick up and drop, use left click to rotate
game.FriendlyFaceOff.How.4: %s First player to finish their puzzle wins!
game.FriendlyFaceOff.Finish2: %1$s managed to finish the image in %2$s seconds
game.FriendlyFaceOff.Finish3: %1$s took %2$s seconds to finish the face
game.HideNPeek.How.Main.1: %s You have 1 minute to get the best spot
game.HideNPeek.How.Main.2: %s Your objective is not to get caught by the seeker, so you can consider the rocking horses your safest bet
game.HideNPeek.How.Main.3: %s The symbol '§c⚠§7' means you're too far from the structure, so you'll get teleported back
game.HideNPeek.How.Solo.1: %s The hiders will have 1 minute to choose a spot
game.HideNPeek.How.Solo.2: %s Once that timer is over you will have 5 chances to find them
game.HideNPeek.How.Solo.3: %s To search in a structure drop your Seeker's Tool near it. If you catch someone they'll start glowing

game.ChannelChangers.How.1: %s Right click a TV to change the channel
game.ChannelChangers.How.2: %s Match each channel to the one displayed at the top
game.ChannelChangers.How.3: %s Match all the channels to win!
game.Shutterpup.How.2: %s Right click to take as many photos of the animal as you can
game.Shutterpup.How.3: %s The player with the most photos containing the animal wins!
